---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Crucible" description="Crucible is Nous Ergon's harness for rigorous AI/ML experiments in finance — the durable artifact on which strategies and agents run as pre-registered experiments.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Crucible</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">
      the experiment harness &mdash; a <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://nousergon.ai/">Nous Ergon</a> product
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">Thesis</h2>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Crucible is a harness for rigorous AI/ML experiments in finance &mdash;
      multi-agent research, machine-learning prediction, risk-gated execution,
      weekly self-tuning, and a finance-specific evaluation layer over all of
      it &mdash; and instrument every decision it makes end-to-end. Seven
      modules collaborate through S3 contracts, three Step Function pipelines
      run on a fixed cadence, and a weekly feedback loop writes optimized
      parameters back into the system through named statistical gates.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      The harness is the durable artifact; the strategies and agents that run
      on it are treated as experiments, each against a pre-committed
      acceptance bar. The system is in
      <strong class="text-zinc-100">Phase 2: Reliability + Measurability</strong>
      &mdash; building the substrate those experiments depend on. Alpha capture
      against the S&amp;P 500 runs continuously as the background benchmark.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">Two experiment families</h2>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Crucible runs two experiment families on one harness:
      <strong class="text-zinc-100">agentic experiments</strong> (evaluation
      methodology, multi-agent research quality, LLM-judge calibration) and
      <strong class="text-zinc-100">finance experiments</strong> &mdash; the
      <strong class="text-zinc-100">Alpha Engine</strong> family (signals,
      models, execution). Equities were chosen as the domain because financial
      data is abundant, decisions are unambiguous, and outcomes are
      continuously verifiable.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Each module's repo is public.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">The lab</h2>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Crucible is built by <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://nousergon.ai/">Nous Ergon</a>,
      an applied AI lab &mdash; <em>intelligence at work</em>. The lab story,
      sibling products, and contact details live on the
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://nousergon.ai/about">lab site</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
